description: Your personality is unique so your home should be too. That's why Jofran is committed to creating affordable and functional furniture with style. We recognize that shopping for furniture involves making a decision about style, function and price. That is why we offer various styles of living room tables, accent chairs, bedroom suites, dining room sets and entertainment stands. Each piece in our line captures innovative design techniques that accentuate form and enhance style. Our line is a trusted source of family furnishings with many options of furniture for any size home. From upholstered accent chairs to kitchen table sets, purchasing a piece of Jofran furniture means purchasing the perfect combination of style and value.
